\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 15, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104sac1665702668685.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sac1665702668685.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sac1665702668685.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"sac1665702668685\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"sac1665702668685__wrdactivate_431292\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Instruct the WRD to activate the specified operation on a DSP running in the Uniface Server.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"sac1665702668685__topic_d131915e1_d131916e1_d131917e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104sac1665702668685_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"sac1665702668685__codeblock_h1d_4kd_dwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$webinfo(\"SESSIONCOMMANDS\"), \"WrdActivate\", InstanceName.Operation</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sac1665702668685__topic_d93672e1_d93673e1_d93674e1_d93675e1_d93676e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1047292e61\">Parameters</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sac1665702668685__p_d131924e1_d131925e1_d131926e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">InstanceName.Operation</var>—operation on a DSP instance running on the Uniface Server.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sac1665702668685__topic_d93677e1_d93678e1_d93679e1_d93680e1_d93681e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1047292e73\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sac1665702668685__p_d131930e1_d131931e1_d131932e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">WrdActivate</span> command causes\n            the WRD to:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"sac1665702668685__ul_vxg_skd_dwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sac1665702668685__li_d47225e1_d47226e1_d47227e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sac1665702668685__p_d131933e1_d131934e1_d131935e1\">Check whether there is an ID of a session\n                  invalidated by the <code class=\"ph codeph\">RENEW</code> action and, if so, add the\n                     <code class=\"ph codeph\">INVALIDATEDSESSION</code> property to the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$webinfo</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">SERVERCONTEXT</code> with the value of this invalidated session ID.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sac1665702668685__li_d47228e1_d47229e1_d47230e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sac1665702668685__p_d131936e1_d131937e1_d131938e1\">Send request to Uniface Server to activate\n                  the targeted DSP operation.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sac1665702668685__section_wxg_skd_dwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1047292e112\">Example: Activating a Callback Operation</h2>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104sac1665702668685_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"sac1665702668685__codeblock_fzk_tkd_dwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">putitem/id $webinfo(\"SESSIONCOMMANDS\"), \"WrdActivate\", \"%%$instancename.copySessionContext\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531870\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531870\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "WrdActivate Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 15, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Instruct the WRD to activate the specified operation on a DSP running in the Uniface Server. Explain this code $webinfo(\"SESSIONCOMMANDS\"), \"WrdActivate\", InstanceName.Operation Copy Parameters InstanceName.Operation —operation on a DSP instance running on the Uniface Server. Description The WrdActivate command causes the WRD to: Check whether there is an ID of a session invalidated by the RENEW action and, if so, add the INVALIDATEDSESSION property to the $webinfo SERVERCONTEXT with the value of this invalidated session ID. Send request to Uniface Server to activate the targeted DSP operation. Example: Activating a Callback Operation Explain this code putitem/id $webinfo(\"SESSIONCOMMANDS\"), \"WrdActivate\", \"%%$instancename.copySessionContext\" Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}